content:
Hi. I need to get in touch with someone at the campaign level who is running the Kamala's Captains. Any suggestions?

Background: I've been working with campain staff for the last month on canvass launches. Today was the first day of Kamala's Captains dry runs, and, despite my month of experience, I was asked to report information that I had no clue how to collect.

I would like to share my experience with someone at the campaign level since the local campaign office says these requests are coming from the campaign and they cannot change it.

Thanks.

This doesn't seem to pertain to what I posted. I've been volunteering every weekend day for the past month and a half. Believe me, I want Harris to win. I'm trying to communicate some issues to the folks in charge so they can be addressed.
I pinged <@1263159708466811000> , a staff member who can help you.
